reviewText: Julie(2004) starring Neha dhupia is the story of a woman who went from being an innocent nave Christian Indian girl living a simple and boring life in a village until she gets into two destructive relationships. First with her boyfriend(Yash Tonk) and then a coworker(Sanjay Kapoor) at a real estate company and then she gets into a very sinful and dangerous profession that she eventually hates and regrets. When she meets millionaire Mihir Shandilya(Priyanshu Chatterjee) her fortunes and bad luck change and she finds true love,happiness and redemption.
